title: Taiwan vessels head to Diaoyu Islands to conduct fishing patrol drills
description: Taiwan's Coast Guard Administration on Thursday sent two ships "Lienchiang" and "Hualien" to waters around the Diaoyu Islands to conduct fishing patrol drills and carry out duty transfer skills.
